{
  "stem": "1975.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 42.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every time-- like we have parties here, and there the party started with drinking, being drunk, and then go out and fight.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was their-- their pastime, basically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now they had a opportunity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have any supervision.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- they felt that suddenly they became the-- the-- the power of the country.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and there was nobody to stop them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were-- they felt they had their arms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had-- they had-- there were the pistols.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had the guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were able to terrorize anybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was actually very difficult to commute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went to-- Incidentally, my parents, before they-- a few months earlier, they were not sure whether they are going to be taken out to Russia.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they brought certain of their goods, like my mother had a very beautiful coat you know, from chinchilla and some other things, they brought that and they left that in in the capital, because they felt it's always-- if they're going to be taken out, they should preserve it.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we took-- took certain things and we took it to my aunt's parents, where they lived on the-- they used to live on this Green Mountain.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so we've-- we came over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when we heard what happened to those people, we came-- we went back to our apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we felt that the safer place was to stay there and and just keep a low visibility.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were also fortunate because the-- the place where we lived, the apartment, the manager, a Lithuanian, was a very nice Lithuanian man who was in his-- I mean, he was older person.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was really in very good-- we-- we had a very good relationship.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
